about a choral foundation.

00:14:39.330 --> 00:14:41.460
&gt;&gt; Nick Brown: Is it
a mixed voice choir?

00:14:41.460 --> 00:14:42.760
&gt;&gt; Peter Phillips: Yes.

00:14:42.760 --> 00:14:46.230
&gt;&gt; Nick Brown: How do you approach
conducting the younger singers

00:14:46.230 --> 00:14:49.140
versus your professional singers?

00:14:49.140 --> 00:14:50.640
&gt;&gt; Peter Phillips:
Well, it's difficult.

00:14:50.640 --> 00:14:56.090
I find conducting inexperienced
singers quite difficult.

00:14:56.090 --> 00:14:58.940
Well, I think they find it quite
difficult to follow me actually.

00:14:58.940 --> 00:15:00.600
