to conduct it sort of sweeping

00:15:19.670 --> 00:15:22.800
through without doing
this heavy downbeat,

00:15:22.800 --> 00:15:26.120
which is what inexperienced
people need.

00:15:26.120 --> 00:15:29.220
They need to know where
the bar starts.

00:15:29.220 --> 00:15:30.520
Well, that's the problem.

00:15:30.520 --> 00:15:33.630
So I've had to sort
of work on that a bit.

00:15:33.630 --> 00:15:38.410 position:56%
The other thing about Merton is that
the -- it's got tremendous acoustics

00:15:38.410 --> 00:15:40.050
and the distances are quite wide.

00:15:40.050 --> 00:15:41.610
It's quite a wide chapel.

00:15:41.610 --> 00:15:44.810
So I'm standing here, and
some of them are over there.

00:15:44.810 --> 00:15:49.650
And I have to sort of
-- that kind of thing.

00:15:49.650 --> 00:15:50.950
Yeah.

