Magnificat is one of them.

00:20:35.150 --> 00:20:37.240
So this evening, we're
singing a Magnificat.

00:20:37.240 --> 00:20:42.240
The Josquin Praeter Rerum
Seriem motet, which is the basis

00:20:42.240 --> 00:20:47.330
