is also a Christmas text --

00:20:47.330 --> 00:20:50.210
very mystical text, wonderful.

00:20:50.210 --> 00:20:52.880
So, but specifically Christmas.

00:20:52.880 --> 00:20:57.440
So it's not quite right
for Advent but, you know.

00:20:57.440 --> 00:20:59.640
You've got some --
