00:21:04.610 --> 00:21:05.910
I mean, that's a giveaway.

00:21:05.910 --> 00:21:08.360
That's not -- yeah.

00:21:08.360 --> 00:21:11.530
&gt;&gt; Nick Brown: Is there anything
in particular in the comparison

00:21:11.530 --> 00:21:15.130 position:56%
