that we should be listening out for?

00:21:15.130 --> 00:21:17.630
&gt;&gt; Peter Phillips: Well,
I have to tell you now --

00:21:17.630 --> 00:21:19.780
okay, here's a bit of a story.

00:21:19.780 --> 00:21:22.030
We're not singing the Salve
Regina by [inaudible].

00:21:22.030 --> 00:21:26.740
Can you recover from
your disappointment?

00:21:26.740 --> 00:21:28.040
&gt;&gt; Nick Brown: Yes.

00:21:28.040 --> 00:21:29.340
Yes.

00:21:29.340 --> 00:21:30.640
&gt;&gt; Peter Phillips:
Thank you very much.

00:21:30.640 --> 00:21:32.530
Because it's just not
a very good piece.

00:21:32.530 --> 00:21:37.800
I'm sorry to put it like that,
but I take risks, you know,

00:21:37.800 --> 00:21:40.310
