there's a Salve Regina there.

00:21:50.630 --> 00:21:52.490
It looks really nice.

00:21:52.490 --> 00:21:56.660
And so I put it down
without ever having heard it.

00:21:56.660 --> 00:21:58.180
But I often do this.

00:21:58.180 --> 00:22:01.250
And these risks usually
come off really nicely.

00:22:01.250 --> 00:22:02.550
But not this time.

00:22:02.550 --> 00:22:03.850
I'm sorry.

00:22:03.850 --> 00:22:06.340
